reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect everyday belt
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the FAIRWIN Ratchet Belt for me and my father, and I must say, it has exceeded our expectations in every way. This belt has quickly become my go-to accessory for its durability, functionality, and stylish design.First and foremost, the ratchet mechanism on this belt is fantastic. Unlike traditional belts with pre-set holes, the ratchet system allows for precise and effortless adjustments to achieve the perfect fit. Whether you need to loosen or tighten the belt, it's as simple as pushing or pulling the buckle, giving you an impeccable fit every time. The automatic buckle works seamlessly, securely locking the belt in place with a satisfying click.The build quality of this belt is exceptional. The tactical nylon material feels sturdy and robust, ensuring that it can withstand daily wear and tear. I've worn it during outdoor activities, and it has held up exceptionally well. The belt is also adjustable, allowing for a wide range of waist sizes. It's great to know that even if my waistline changes, this belt will still provide a comfortable fit.One of the standout features of this belt is its versatility. It's designed to be a golf belt but works equally well with jeans and other casual outfits. The sleek design and the range of available colors make it suitable for various occasions. Whether I'm heading to the office, going out for a round of golf, or enjoying a casual weekend, this belt seamlessly complements my attire.Furthermore, this FAIRWIN Ratchet Belt offers an excellent value for the money. Compared to other high-end belts on the market, it delivers the same level of quality without breaking the bank. The fact that it comes with an automatic buckle adds an extra layer of convenience and sophistication.In conclusion, the FAIRWIN Ratchet Belt has proven to be a reliable and versatile accessory. Its ratchet mechanism, durable construction, and stylish design make it a must-have for any man's wardrobe. Whether you're looking for a belt for daily use or special occasions, this belt ticks all the boxes. I highly recommend it to anyone in need of a dependable and fashionable belt option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Slips excessively on a portly size
reviews.reviewText: Overall I like the belt. Its nylon construction is sturdy enough. The problem I have is that it constantly slips and I have to constantly be retightening it. Wish the buckle would grip more agressively instead of relatively easily slipping from its assigned location, thus needing constant adjustment.FOLLOW UP TO REVIEW: The FAIRWIN customer service team contacted me after I posted my review. They went above and beyond to correct the problem I was having with the belt I had purchased, something that is rarely done by any other company. I was pleasantly surprised by their attention and solution to this matter, I highly recommend this company's products and their excellent customer service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Belt for IWB C. Carry
reviews.reviewText: I like this belt for so many reasons: looks nice, fits great, and after wearing for 3+ weeks it feels like it will last a long time. I bought this belt for iwb conceal carry and I have put this under some serious testing and it WORKS GREAT. It holds everything secure with my 45, extra mags, and knife/tool. The belt is thicker than an average belt so my holster stays SECURELY on the belt during every draw, even if I incorrectly attach the holster.If by chance your holster or something hits the release lever on the buckle, it only releases to the next notch on the belt but still holds secure and its easy & quick to re ratchet the belt. Again, this is an issue I found during testing or having the belt too tight.If I ever need a new belt, I would purchase this belt again.
